Description:
Grep is a grep library written in java. It allows to look for a pattern in a
given (set of) file(s).

Compilation:
No specific compilation tricks.
You can do something like: 
$ cd src/
$ javac -d ../bin/ com/jde/grep/Grep.java

Usage:
There is a main to show you how to use it. But you can also use it as a library in
your own apps.



